          </p>
          <div class="download">
            <a href="#">contact</a>
            <p>download CV <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i></p>
          </div>
          <br><br><br>
          <div class="icon">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/login"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in" ></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></i></a>
